replyContent:
In the upper right corner of the game screen, you will find the Exit to Main Menu button.
When you enter the main menu, you will find a cog wheel button on the bottom.
Press it. The Options menu screen appears.
There is a bar at the bottom where you can adjust the scroll speed of text.
I hope my answer helps.
Have fun. :)
